      <abstract>
        <p>Taller Than a Dwarf, a Broadway comedy, announces closing (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Taller Than a Dwarf,'' a comedy by Elaine May, is to close after the matinee on Sunday at the Longacre Theater, 220 West 48th Street, Manhattan. Directed by Alan Arkin and starring Matthew Broderick and Parker Posey, the play will have run for 56 regular performances and 37 previews.</p>
      </block>
